&lt;p&gt;P + Q: P is the daughter of Q.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Q &amp;divide; R: Q is the father of R.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;R &amp;times; S: R is the wife of S.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;S - T: S is the brother of T.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage681b5493fe389625c30a3ed1.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thus, P is &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;brother&amp;#39;s wife&amp;#39;s sister&lt;/span&gt; of T.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Option 2&amp;quot;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

