&lt;p&gt;F is sitting to the immediate right of G and the immediate left of D.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;E is sitting to the immediate right of D. A is sitting second to the right of E. B is sitting second to the left of C.&lt;/p&gt;

