&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;R&amp;nbsp;does not sit at any of the extreme ends.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;The one who faces N, sits to the immediate left of P.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Now, case 2 gets eliminated as Q cannot sit&amp;nbsp;immediate right of S&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

