&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Given:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Expression: [(91 &amp;divide; 7) &amp;times; {(64 &amp;divide; 4) + (17 &amp;divide; 6) &amp;times; (8 - 2)}]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Formula Used:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Order of operations (BODMAS): Solve inside brackets first, then division/multiplication, and finally addition/subtraction.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Calculation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; [(91 &amp;divide; 7) &amp;times; {(64 &amp;divide; 4) + (17 &amp;divide; 6) &amp;times; (8 - 2)}]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; (13) &amp;times; {(16) + (17 &amp;divide; 6) &amp;times; (6)}&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; (13) &amp;times; {16 + (17 &amp;times; 6 &amp;divide; 6)}&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; (13) &amp;times; {16 + 17}&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; 13 &amp;times; 33&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; 429&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;there4; The value of [(91 &amp;divide; 7) &amp;times; {(64 &amp;divide; 4) + (17 &amp;divide; 6) &amp;times; (8 - 2)}] is 429.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

