	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;To ensure grammatical correctness, the adverb &amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;heavily&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;quot; should be used instead of the adjective &amp;quot;heavy.&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
