	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Biting the bullet&lt;/strong&gt; (‡§ó‡§Ç‡§≠‡•Ä‡§∞ ‡§∏‡•ç‡§•‡§ø‡§§‡§ø ‡§ï‡•ã ‡§∏‡§π‡§® ‡§ï‡§∞‡§®‡§æ): To face a difficult or unpleasant situation with courage.

