	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Hence, we can infer that the most appropriate idiom for maximizing advantages in negotiations is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;play his cards right&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
