&lt;p&gt;Here are the other options explained along with their Hindi meanings and example sentences:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Play it safe&lt;/strong&gt; (&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;‡§∏‡§æ‡§µ‡§ß‡§æ‡§®‡•Ä ‡§∏‡•á ‡§ñ‡•á‡§≤‡§®‡§æ&lt;/span&gt;): Acting cautiously and avoiding risks.

	&lt;ul&gt;
