	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Play it by ear&lt;/strong&gt; (&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;‡§Ö‡§®‡•Å‡§Æ‡§æ‡§® ‡§ï‡•á ‡§Ü‡§ß‡§æ‡§∞ ‡§™‡§∞ ‡§ï‡§æ‡§∞‡•ç‡§Ø ‡§ï‡§∞‡§®‡§æ&lt;/span&gt;): To act spontaneously and according to the situation without a fixed plan.
