&lt;p&gt;Here are the other options explained along with their Hindi meanings and example sentences:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Panic&lt;/strong&gt; (‡§ò‡§¨‡§∞‡§æ‡§π‡§ü): A sudden overwhelming fear or anxiety that may cause irrational behaviour.

	&lt;ul&gt;
