	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt; The artist&amp;#39;s paintings were &lt;strong&gt;displayed &lt;/strong&gt;at the gallery last weekend.&lt;/li&gt;
