	&lt;li&gt;The word &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Opaque&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; means not allowing light to pass through; it is something that is not transparent or clear. (‡§Ö‡§™‡§æ‡§∞‡§¶‡§∞‡•ç‡§∂‡•Ä)

